OL,3,CConsumer confidence rises slightly
OL,4,Cfollowing signs of Iran 'de-escalation'
OL,6,F"Cutting these charges is the fastest
OL,7,Fway to ease inflation and support
OL,8,Fconsumer confidence.
OL,10,F"Delay will only make the next cost of
OL,11,Fliving squeeze harder for households."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@fO]
